  • Constructor Details

    • SpaceMarine

      public SpaceMarine(String name, Coordinates coordinates, Double health, int heartCount, AstartesCategory category, MeleeWeapon meleeWeapon, Chapter chapter, long id, Date creationDate)
      Constructs a new SpaceMarine object. Used only for reading collection from CSV file.
      Parameters:
      name - Element's name.
      coordinates - Element's coordinates.
      health - Value of element's health.
      heartCount - Value of element's heartCount.
      category - category of the element.
      meleeWeapon - meleeWeapon of the element.
      chapter - chapter of the element.
      id - Element's id.
      creationDate - Element's creationDate.
      Throws:
      WrongFieldException - if id or health or heart count is less than or equal to 0 or heart count is greater than 3
      NullFieldException - if name or coordinates or chapter is null.

    • SpaceMarine

      public SpaceMarine(String name, Coordinates coordinates, Double health, int heartCount, AstartesCategory category, MeleeWeapon meleeWeapon, Chapter chapter)
      Constructs a new SpaceMarine object. Used to create element by user because id and creation date are autogenerated.
      Parameters:
      name - Element's name. Cannot be null or empty and cannot contain commas.
      coordinates - Element's coordinates(Coordinates). Cannot be null.
      health - Value of element's health. Can be null. Must be greater than 0.
      heartCount - Value of element's heartCount. Must be greater than 0 and less than or equal to 3.
      category - category(AstartesCategory) of the element. Can be null.
      meleeWeapon - meleeWeapon(MeleeWeapon) of the element. Can be null.
      chapter - chapter(Chapter) of the element. Cannot be null.
      Throws:
      WrongFieldException - if health or heart count is less than or equal to 0 or heart count is greater than 3
      NullFieldException - if name or coordinates or chapter is null.
